	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>OK i am posting this question on every hybrid and bard forumn here, who are better soloers?<br><br>Shadowknights-fearkiteing, DoTs, Pets, Absorbs<br><br>Paladins-Fearkite undead, healing, ac/hp buffs<br><br>Rangers-Kiteing, root-archery, track, dualweild&nbsp;&nbsp; heal, buffs<br><br>Bards-crappy heal songs, crappy dd/dot songs, haste and buff songs, and dual weild<br><br>I know Necro's and Druids are the  best soloers but i want to be a hybrid so if anyone has any suggestions thanks.<br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
	     <tr><td colspan=2 align=right class=mform id=fs8>4 Replies</td></tr>
